UserObject.plantUmlData:
{
  "data": "@startuml
skinparam monochrome true

actor User as U
participant HomeView as HV
participant SimpleRequestService as SRS
collections SimpleRequestDTOs as SRDTO
participant SimpleRequestTourService as SRTS
participant SimpleRequestTourRepository as SRTR
participant SimpleRequestRepository as SRR
collections Locations as L

U -> HV++: Log in
HV -> SRDTO**: <<create>> SuggestionNotifications
HV -> SRS ++: CreateSuggestionNotificationsByGuest2(user)

   SRS -> SRS ++: CreateNotifications()
      SRS -> SRDTO : <<Create>> simpleRequestTourDTOs
      SRS -> SRTS ++ : GetAll()
         SRTS -> SRTR ++ : GetAll()
         SRTR --> SRTS --: allSimpleRequestTours
      SRTS --> SRS --: simpleRequestTours

      loop foreach simpleRequestTour in simpleRequestTours
      SRS -> SRDTO ++: Add(simpleRequestTourDTO)
      SRDTO --> SRS --:
      deactivate SRDTO 
      end
   SRS --> SRS --: notifications

   SRS -> SRS ++: GetInvalidRequestsLocationsForGuest2(user)
      SRS -> L**: <<Create>> locations
      SRS -> SRR ++: GetAllByGuest2(user)
      SRR --> SRS --: simpleRequests
      loop foreach simpleRequest in simpleRequests
         opt simpleRequest.Status == SimpleRequestStatus.INVALID
         SRS -> L++: Add(simpleRequest.location)
         L --> SRS --:
         deactivate L
         end
      end
   SRS --> SRS --: invalidRequestLocations

   SRS -> SRS ++: GetInvlaidRequestsLanguagesForGuest2(user)
      SRS -> SRR ++: GetAllByGuest2(user)
      SRR --> SRS --: simpleRequests
      
      loop foreach simpleRequest in simpleRequests
         opt simpleRequest.Status == SimpleRequestStatus.INVALID
         SRS -> SRS++: languages.add(simpleRequest.language)
         deactivate SRS
         end
      end
   SRS --> SRS --: invalidRequestsLanguages

   SRS -> SRDTO : <<Create>> suggestionNotifications
      loop foreach notification in notifications
         opt notification.SimpleRequest.Status == SimpleRequestStatus.APPROVED && notification.SimpleRequest.User.Id != user.Id
            SRS -> SRS ++: CheckRequestCompatibility(invalidRequestLocations, invalidRequestsLanguages, suggestionNotifications, notification)
               SRS -> L ++: <<create>> notificationLocation
               L --> SRS --:

               SRS -> SRS ++: containsLocation
                  loop foreach location in invalidRequestLocations
                     opt location.State.Equals(notificationLocation.State) && location.City.Equals(notificationLocation.City)
                  SRS --> SRS: true
                     end
                  
                  end
                  SRS --> SRS --: false

               SRS -> SRS ++: containsLanguage
                  loop foreach language in invalidRequestsLanguages
                     opt language.Equals(notification.Tour.Language)
                  SRS --> SRS: true
                     end
                  
                  end
                  SRS --> SRS --: false
               
               opt containsLocation || containsLanguage
                 SRS -> SRDTO++: Add(notification)
                 deactivate SRS
                 SRDTO --> SRS --:
               end

            deactivate SRS 
         end
      end

SRS --> HV --: SuggestionNotifications
HV --> U --: Display Suggested notifications


@enduml",
  "format": "svg"
}
